description: This latest version V1.4 six foot long HDMI cable is fully HDCP compliant, and HDMI Authority certified, providing the highest levels of performance as well as being compatible with all HD formats and resolutions, including 480p/480i/720p/1080i and 1080p. Our cables also Version 1.3 compliant. This cable supports 10.2Gbps bandwidth not just 5Gbps of other low priced cables.
title: Fanatic Digital Imperial Series Gold-Plated HDMI Cable (6 feet)
